  "title": "Restaurant Captain",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Greeting and seating guests</strong> in a warm and professional manner.</li><li><a href=\"https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=7a423d98da7f356edf13039322ca326a72c97afadabf81b4249332031d2f1beeJmltdHM9MTc2OTQ3MjAwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=018add51-6202-679b-08a2-cf7f633a6651&psq=restaurant+captain&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubXljYXJlZXJzZnV0dXJlLmdvdi5zZy9qb2IvZm9vZC1hbmQtYmV2ZXJhZ2UvcmVzdGF1cmFudC1jYXB0YWluLWFpc2EtY2FmZS1hNjhmY2M1ZDhhOTM4OTZjNjQwNTFmYzMwN2VmNzI3Nw&ntb=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Taking initial orders</strong> for food and beverages, including cocktails, wine, and other drinks, and recommending pairings</a></li><li><strong>Serving food and beverages</strong> efficiently according to service standards.</li><li><strong>Coordinating with the kitchen</strong> to communicate orders, special dietary needs, or wait times.</li><li><a href=\"https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=4880f1905cc63e0f1d15fd38e06fcebeeeac48054c63c5ac70be98b855baed28JmltdHM9MTc2OTQ3MjAwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=018add51-6202-679b-08a2-cf7f633a6651&psq=restaurant+captain&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9zZy5qb2JzdHJlZXQuY29tL3Jlc3RhdXJhbnQtY2FwdGFpbi1qb2Jz&ntb=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Supervising service staff</strong>, ensuring workflow efficiency, providing guidance, and assisting with on-the-job training </a><a href=\"https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=4880f1905cc63e0f1d15fd38e06fcebeeeac48054c63c5ac70be98b855baed28JmltdHM9MTc2OTQ3MjAwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=018add51-6202-679b-08a2-cf7f633a6651&psq=restaurant+captain&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9zZy5qb2JzdHJlZXQuY29tL3Jlc3RhdXJhbnQtY2FwdGFpbi1qb2Jz&ntb=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2</strong></a>.</li><li><strong>Handling point-of-sale (POS) transactions</strong> accurately and maintaining records of orders.</li><li><strong>Maintaining cleanliness and presentation standards</strong> across tables and service areas throughout the shift.</li><li><strong>Monitoring guest satisfaction</strong>, addressing concerns promptly and maintaining a positive dining experience.</li></ul><h2>Skills and Qualifications</h2><ul><li>Excellent <strong>communication and interpersonal skills</strong> to interact with guests and staff.</li><li>Strong <strong>leadership abilities</strong> to manage and motivate the team.</li><li>In-depth <strong>knowledge of the menu, beverages, and service techniques</strong>.</li><li>Ability to multitask and anticipate guest needs.</li><li>Familiarity with <strong>POS systems</strong> and basic operational workflows<a href=\"https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=7a423d98da7f356edf13039322ca326a72c97afadabf81b4249332031d2f1beeJmltdHM9MTc2OTQ3MjAwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=018add51-6202-679b-08a2-cf7f633a6651&psq=restaurant+captain&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubXljYXJlZXJzZnV0dXJlLmdvdi5zZy9qb2IvZm9vZC1hbmQtYmV2ZXJhZ2UvcmVzdGF1cmFudC1jYXB0YWluLWFpc2EtY2FmZS1hNjhmY2M1ZDhhOTM4OTZjNjQwNTFmYzMwN2VmNzI3Nw&ntb=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=7a423d98da7f356edf13039322ca326a72c97afadabf81b4249332031d2f1beeJmltdHM9MTc2OTQ3MjAwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=018add51-6202-679b-08a2-cf7f633a6651&psq=restaurant+captain&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubXljYXJlZXJzZnV0dXJlLmdvdi5zZy9qb2IvZm9vZC1hbmQtYmV2ZXJhZ2UvcmVzdGF1cmFudC1jYXB0YWluLWFpc2EtY2FmZS1hNjhmY2M1ZDhhOTM4OTZjNjQwNTFmYzMwN2VmNzI3Nw&ntb=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong></strong></a></li></ul><p></p><p></p><p><strong></strong></p><p></p><p></p>",
